OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FTeachers working 12-hour   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fdays, leaked report says   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Almost a quarter of teachers in England
OL,6, are working 12-hour days, according to 
OL,7, a leaked government report.            
OL,9,FSome 22% of teachers said they were    
OL,10,Fworking 60 hours a week or more.       
OL,12,FThe research, commissioned by the      
OL,13,FDepartment for Education (DfE), was    
OL,14,Fcarried out in Spring 2022 and has not 
OL,15,Fyet been made public.                  
OL,17,FEducation Secretary Gillian Keegan has 
OL,18,Fsaid a new taskforce will be created to
OL,19,Fhelp reduce teachers' workload by an   
OL,20,Faverage five hours a week.             
